======================================================================
                  TakyonDB Dual-Licensing Model
======================================================================

TakyonDB is distributed under a dual-licensing model to support both
open-source developers and commercial enterprises:

1. Open Source License (GNU AGPLv3)
   Free for independent developers, students, and open-source projects. 
   Under the AGPLv3, if you modify and run TakyonDB as part of a 
   network service (SaaS), you MUST release the source code of your 
   entire application stack to your users under the AGPLv3.

2. Commercial License ($10 / month)
   For companies and closed-source projects that do not wish to 
   open-source their proprietary code. By purchasing the commercial 
   license, you are granted an explicit legal exception to the AGPLv3. 
   This allows you to use TakyonDB in a commercial/private network 
   setting without any copyleft obligations to share your source code.

For commercial licensing, please visit our website.

